genresAdvancedInfo.name: pittsburgh rock
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Pittsburgh rock is a dynamic and eclectic genre that encompasses a wide range of styles, from classic and hard rock to punk and indie. It is characterized by its raw energy, catchy melodies, and introspective lyrics, often inspired by the city's unique urban landscape and working-class ethos.
